Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It blasted a massive hole\Nin the spectator area!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burgess's terrific Shockwave Elbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upstart pirate - Blackbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ten Titanic Captains are supporting him!\NAnd one of them is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jesus Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That bastard!\N--Don't involve the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How destructive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another Fighting Fish\Ncharging towards the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the "01" Fighting Fish \Ncarrying the Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going for Bartolomeo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's made a turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it going for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, oh my! The other Fighting Fish are\Nsurfacing one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to be all-out battle between
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe contenders in the ring and the Fighting Fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These fish will never learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charging at me?\NYou must be out of your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no business with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the "01" Fighting Fish targeting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's going for Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the survival of the fittest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the mechanism of the natural world\Nthat the weak fall prey first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've set its sights on her\Nfrom the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta cut the chain at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! The battle \Nbetween Lucy and Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight you next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have the Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring you down\Nalong with that fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burgess is gonna do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Run!\N--He's gonna do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How smart of you to stand behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna try to get away? Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shockwave...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, oh my! Burgess's armor \Nhas shattered into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Only he could done that!\NMy great {\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna just give up\Nthe Flare-Flare Fruit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His fighting style has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all in another league!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you\Nto win that competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have courage to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to attack like I'm willing to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\NOr I have no chance of winning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san, I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...going to do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's our commander!\N--Alright! We're taking control of the lift now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you do have some fight in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I know that voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've hijacked the lift\Nand what are you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take down Doflamingo\Nand restore the King Riku dynasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:01.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,LAO G\NTHE DON QUIXOTE FAMILY\N (THE DIAMANTE ARMY)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cub-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!\NYou couldn't see what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect one of the Executives\Nto be in the lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was ordered to stand guard\Nat the entrance of the Toy House,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to take the lift downwards and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,waited ready at the entrance \Nof the underground trade port
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but got on the lift again.\NIn other words, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...took the wron"g" lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's "G"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you reach the palace! Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE RAMPART TOWER B-1\NLUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, barely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec! I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's such a pain!\N--Let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style - 108 Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use hitting those walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:21.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE RAMPART TOWER B-2\NKIN'EMON'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stairs that we were going down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...suddenly bent upwards like \Nthey're leading to the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were heading to the Toy House underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go any farther like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually good we were stopped here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get to the Toy House below,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to go up to the palace first
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then take the lift downwards. \NThat's the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go up in order to go down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means we didn't have to split up\Nfrom Luffy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, we didn't!\N--Why didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to tell you many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--To go down...\N--Stay inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know what to do\Nif you fell out of there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while I was unaware!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are all such blockheads,\Njumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No, no!\NWe shouldn't be fighting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can get to the lift in the palace,\Nthe security is tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can get on but\Nsince you're a Big Human...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if they couldn't figure out\Nwho I truly was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:22.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE TOY HOUSE - FRANKY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys taking such a long time\Nto kill one guy-{\i1}dara{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the big fish is coming in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself-{\i1}dara{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Bastille-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why is the Navy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NDon't tell me it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take me down that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pay you back double!\NPrepare for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave it to the Navy as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted to hear!\NCan I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's just a robot,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is a pervert, just as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Señor! You're so hard-boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away from the stone man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna go down easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, take her and go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:22:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead and kick Doflamingo's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This stone guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…is gonna get cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
